              <h3>LEXICON: LEGAL TERMS OF HOUSING LAW AND REAL ESTATE LAW</h3>
              <p class="back_to_overview">Anyone who is inexperienced in real estate usually has problems understanding the large number of legal terms whose definitions are not known.</p>
              <p>To provide a little more clarity and understanding, we have put together a lexicon of various legal terms - from commonly known words for beginners to specific expressions for special topics. Each term is briefly explained, for more information just click on the respective word, then you will get to a detailed article</p>
